net.sf.jclec.mo.distance

Class ManhattanDistance

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.mo.distance.ManhattanDistance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.jclec.IDistance

    public class ManhattanDistance
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.sf.jclec.IDistance
    Manhattan distance between two individuals in the objective space. The distance is computed extracting the objective values from the fitness object of each individual. MOFitness objects are expected.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
    IDistance, MOFitness
